 25870	      }
 25871	
 25872	      /* End of ManualSwitch: '<S2>/Manual Switch2' */
 25873	
 25874	      /* ManualSwitch: '<S2>/Manual Switch4' incorporates:
 25875	       *  Constant: '<S2>/Constant'
 25876	       */
 25877	      if (m_ModelParameters.ManualSwitch4_CurrentSetting == 1) {
 25878	        m_BlockIO.ManualSwitch4[i] = m_BlockIO.tau_f_model[i];
 25879	      } else {
 25880	        m_BlockIO.ManualSwitch4[i] = m_ModelParameters.Constant_Value[i];
 25881	      }
 25882	
 25883	      /* End of ManualSwitch: '<S2>/Manual Switch4' */
 25884	
 25885	      /* Sum: '<S2>/Add2' */
 25886	      m_BlockIO.Add2[i] = m_BlockIO.Add[i] + m_BlockIO.ManualSwitch4[i];
 25887	    }
 25888	
 25889	    srUpdateBC(m_DWork.FrictionCompensation_SubsysRanBC);
 25890	  }
 25891	
 25892	  /* End of Constant: '<Root>/FictionCompensationEnabled' */
 25893	  /* End of Outputs for SubSystem: '<Root>/Friction Compensation' */
 25894	  for (i = 0; i < 7; i++) {
 25895	    /* Sum: '<Root>/Add' */
 25896	    m_BlockIO.Add[i] = m_BlockIO.tau_singularperturbation[i] +
 25897	      m_BlockIO.Add2[i];
 25898	
 25899	    /* Outport: '<Root>/fast_control_motor_torque' */
 25900	    m_Output.fast_control_motor_torque[i] = m_BlockIO.Add[i];
 25901	  }
 25902	
 25903	  /* MATLAB Function: '<Root>/Robot Pose Logger' incorporates:
 25904	   *  Inport: '<Root>/sensor_mft_application_button'
 25905	   */
 25906	  /* MATLAB Function 'Robot Pose Logger': '<S5>:1' */
 25907	  /* '<S5>:1:4' if(isempty(last_application_button)) */
 25908	  if (!m_DWork.last_application_button_not_empty) {
 25909	    /* '<S5>:1:5' last_application_button=application_button; */
 25910	    m_DWork.last_application_button =
 25911	      m_Input.sensor_mft_application_button;
 25912	    m_DWork.last_application_button_not_empty = true;
 25913	  }
 25914	
 25915	  /* '<S5>:1:8' if(last_application_button~=application_button && application_button) */
 25916	  if ((m_DWork.last_application_button !=
 25917	       m_Input.sensor_mft_application_button) &&
 25918	      (m_Input.sensor_mft_application_button != 0.0)) {
 25919	    /* '<S5>:1:9' fprintf('[%.10f,%.10f,%.10f,%.10f;%.10f,%.10f,%.10f,%.10f;%.10f,%.10f,%.10f,%.10f],...',... */
 25920	    /* '<S5>:1:10'       robot_model.H(1,1),robot_model.H(1,2),robot_model.H(1,3),robot_model.H(1,4),... */
 25921	    /* '<S5>:1:11'       robot_model.H(2,1),robot_model.H(2,2),robot_model.H(2,3),robot_model.H(2,4),... */
 25922	    /* '<S5>:1:12'       robot_model.H(3,1),robot_model.H(3,2),robot_model.H(3,3),robot_model.H(3,4)); */
 25923	    printf("[%.10f,%.10f,%.10f,%.10f;%.10f,%.10f,%.10f,%.10f;%.10f,%.10f,%.10f,%.10f],...",
 25924	           m_BlockIO.robot_model_g.H[0], m_BlockIO.robot_model_g.H[4],
 25925	           m_BlockIO.robot_model_g.H[8], m_BlockIO.robot_model_g.H[12],
 25926	           m_BlockIO.robot_model_g.H[1], m_BlockIO.robot_model_g.H[5],
 25927	           m_BlockIO.robot_model_g.H[9], m_BlockIO.robot_model_g.H[13],
 25928	           m_BlockIO.robot_model_g.H[2], m_BlockIO.robot_model_g.H[6],
 25929	           m_BlockIO.robot_model_g.H[10], m_BlockIO.robot_model_g.H[14]);
 25930	    fflush(stdout);
 25931	  }
 25932	
 25933	  /* '<S5>:1:15' last_application_button=application_button; */
 25934	  m_DWork.last_application_button =
 25935	    m_Input.sensor_mft_application_button;
 25936	
 25937	  /* End of MATLAB Function: '<Root>/Robot Pose Logger' */
 25938	
 25939	  /* Outport: '<Root>/MotionEnable' incorporates:
 25940	   *  Constant: '<Root>/MotionEnableValue'
 25941	   */
 25942	  m_Output.MotionEnable = m_ModelParameters.MotionEnableValue_Value;
 25943	
 25944	  /* Outport: '<Root>/MotionDisable' incorporates:
 25945	   *  Constant: '<Root>/MotionDisableValue'
 25946	   */
 25947	  m_Output.MotionDisable = m_ModelParameters.MotionDisableValue_Value;
 25948	
 25949	  /* Outport: '<Root>/fast_control_motor_enable' incorporates:
 25950	   *  Constant: '<Root>/Constant10'
 25951	   *  Constant: '<Root>/Constant22'
 25952	   *  Constant: '<Root>/Constant23'
 25953	   *  Constant: '<Root>/Constant4'
 25954	   *  Constant: '<Root>/Constant7'
 25955	   *  Constant: '<Root>/Constant8'
 25956	   *  Constant: '<Root>/Constant9'
 25957	   */
 25958	  m_Output.fast_control_motor_enable[0] = m_ModelParameters.Constant22_Value;
 25959	  m_Output.fast_control_motor_enable[1] = m_ModelParameters.Constant4_Value;
 25960	  m_Output.fast_control_motor_enable[2] = m_ModelParameters.Constant7_Value;
 25961	  m_Output.fast_control_motor_enable[3] = m_ModelParameters.Constant8_Value;
 25962	  m_Output.fast_control_motor_enable[4] = m_ModelParameters.Constant9_Value;
 25963	  m_Output.fast_control_motor_enable[5] = m_ModelParameters.Constant10_Value;
 25964	  m_Output.fast_control_motor_enable[6] = m_ModelParameters.Constant23_Value;
 25965	}
 25966	
 25967	void Ccontroller::controller_update (void)
 25968	{
 25969	  /* Update absolute time for base rate */
 25970	  /* The "clockTick0" counts the number of times the code of this task has
 25971	   * been executed. The absolute time is the multiplication of "clockTick0"
 25972	   * and "Timing.stepSize0". Size of "clockTick0" ensures timer will not
 25973	   * overflow during the application lifespan selected.
 25974	   * Timer of this task consists of two 32 bit unsigned integers.
 25975	   * The two integers represent the low bits Timing.clockTick0 and the high bits
 25976	   * Timing.clockTickH0. When the low bit overflows to 0, the high bits increment.
 25977	   */
 25978	  if (!(++(&m_SimStruct)->Timing.clockTick0)) {
 25979	    ++(&m_SimStruct)->Timing.clockTickH0;
 25980	  }
 25981	
 25982	  (&m_SimStruct)->Timing.t[0] = (&m_SimStruct)->Timing.clockTick0 *
 25983	    (&m_SimStruct)->Timing.stepSize0 + (&m_SimStruct)->Timing.clockTickH0 *
 25984	    (&m_SimStruct)->Timing.stepSize0 * 4294967296.0;
 25985	}
